    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is acknowledged and accepted given that the ASTM F1717 protocol is a standardized regulatory test method with fixed loading conditions, and the model's predictive accuracy is robustly demonstrated across all three QoIs with E/uval well below the 1.96 threshold. The medium model risk level and medium decision consequence are consistent with the evidence package provided.",
